window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>With the rest of the world in shambles, Tav, his women, and their growing community are surviving. Against all odds and much opposition, they have managed to create some order amidst the chaos. </p> <p>But winter is coming, and the threat of untold hordes of hungry mouths sweeping through and destroying their community is bearing down on them. </p> <p>They must stockpile and fortify, because when the snow falls and people get desperate, only the strong and prepared will survive.</p>"; 
